column5: Hey... I'm looking into setting up a live fish cam feed for a client of mine... anybody know where I can find some examples.. I know they had one on the St Marys river.. any on know of any others??
St Marys Cam  Im pretty sure the Soo cam is in the sturgeon tanks for the winter. It will be back in the river soon.

heres a link to a wolf river fish cam live feed...Ha been watching it for 1/2 hour now...I'm entranced  http://www.ustream.tv/channel/wolfrivercam-2  theres actually a few more on there if you search around TJ
